msgctxt "0001"
msgid "A bird in the hand is worth two in the bush."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0002"
msgid "...Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0003"
msgid "It's a proverb."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0004"
msgid ""
"It means if you can only obtain something inferior,\n"
"that's still better than longing for something better."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0005"
msgid "Yeah, I know what it means. But...so what?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0006"
msgid ""
"Put another way, if all you have nearby is a loser,\n"
"that's better than a proper assistant far away."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0007"
msgid "Makoto. Be my secretary."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0008"
msgid "What...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0009"
msgid ""
"A useless commoner like you could never hope to earn\n"
"more than, say, 100,000 dollars a year."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0010"
msgid ""
"But as my secretary, you would be guaranteed an ample\n"
"salary and job security for the rest of your life."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0011"
msgid "And in honor of it being my birthday today..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0012"
msgid ""
"...how about I multiply your already impossible\n"
"expectations by, oh, 5.5?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0013"
msgid "550,000 dollars?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0014"
msgid "5.5 million dollars?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0015"
msgid "What!? You wanna pay me 5.5 million dollars a year!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0016"
msgid "You'd better check your math on that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0017"
msgid "Gh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0018"
msgid ""
"Or is that a request? I could pay you that kind of\n"
"salary, but..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0019"
msgid ""
"...I would have to raise my expectations for you\n"
"accordingly."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0020"
msgid "Y-Yeah, I was just kidding!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0021"
msgid "I don't wanna do the math"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0022"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>100,000 dollars times 5.5? I'm afraid to even do the\n"
"math on that...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0023"
msgid ""
"What? Did your brain freeze up trying to comprehend\n"
"that much money?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0024"
msgid "Y-Yeah, something like that..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0025"
msgid ""
"Regardless, it's on you. I can't draw up a contract\n"
"until you name your price."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0026"
msgid ""
"What's the matter? Are you so surprised you're about\n"
"to faint where you stand?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0027"
msgid "Well, whenever you wake up, name your price."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0028"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>100,000 dollars times 5.5? You mean...?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0029"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>550,000 dollars!? That's like, board member money!\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0030"
msgid ""
"Of course, as my secretary you wouldn't be\n"
"a mere servant."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0031"
msgid ""
"At some point, I would want you to become an actual\n"
"assistant, taking the lead on important projects."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0032"
msgid ""
"Assuming you produce acceptable results, you could\n"
"even become a core part of the Togami Corporation."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0033"
msgid "You have no reason to refuse."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0034"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>This is all so sudden... I don't get why... But he\n"
"seems serious about it...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0035"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Still, I...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0036"
msgid "I'm sorry, but I'm gonna hafta say no."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0037"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgctxt "0038"
msgid ""
"I'm trying to give you a chance to enter the\n"
"battlefield of life and claim victory."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0039"
msgid ""
"Most commoners will never get that chance. This is\n"
"literally a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0040"
msgid "Do you understand? This is your chance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0041"
msgid ""
"This is your one and only chance to rise above the\n"
"99%."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0042"
msgid ""
"Are you really so scared of having to fight,\n"
"to compete, in order to win?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0043"
msgid "It's not that I'm scared..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0044"
msgid ""
"It's that I want to succeed based on my own effort.\n"
"I want to find my own battlefield..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0045"
msgid "I don't want it handed to meâ€”I want to earn it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0046"
msgid ""
"I want to find something I'm willing to fight and die\n"
"for. That's the only way I'll be satisfied."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0047"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgctxt "0048"
msgid "Then you meant what you said earlier..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0049"
msgid ""
"That if you can live a life that you're satisfied\n"
"with, that's all that matters..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0050"
msgid "Hmm... I'm glad to see you passed my test."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0051"
msgid "Huh? Your test?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0052"
msgid ""
"That's right. The mere thought of someone like you as\n"
"my secretary makes me physically ill."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0053"
msgid "Wait, so then..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0054"
msgid ""
"The salary offer still stands, of course. It's yours\n"
"if you want it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0055"
msgid ""
"I don't need you spreading rumors that Byakuya Togami\n"
"doesn't honor his word."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0056"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>So he'd basically be paying me...to do nothing?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0057"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>In a way...I almost regret my decision.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0058"
msgid "But I must say, I just don't understand you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0059"
msgid ""
"You don't want to fight, and yet you don't flee from\n"
"the battle, either."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0060"
msgid "It's like I said..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0061"
msgid ""
"For me, happiness comes from <CLT 3>living the life I want\n"
"to live<CLT>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0062"
msgid "Hmph. Easy enough to say."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0063"
msgid "Now you have to enforce your will until the very end."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0064"
msgid ""
"If you can do that, if you can make it to the end, I'm\n"
"afraid I'll be forced to acknowledge you..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0065"
msgid "Then that's exactly what I'll do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0066"
msgid "Someday, absolutely..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0067"
msgid "I don't expect much from you, but I'll be waiting."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0068"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Byakuya's <CLT><CLT 3>Report Card<CLT><CLT 23> has been updated based on your\n"
"experience with him.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0069"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Your maximum number of <CLT><CLT 3>Skill Points<CLT><CLT 23> has increased!\n"
"Hey, look at you go!\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0070"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Once we were all done, I headed back to my room for a\n"
"little while...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""
